{"tid":996161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國旅客攜非洲豬瘟食品入境日本","createTime":"2019-01-26T05:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T09:08:27.000Z","uid":31341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d6a5ce3f333ede1c873b7bf013d79690bf128c","tid":996161,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=335560&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335560%26refer%3DShare&d=5LGFuo5nUsA%2Bmel9t3wDT7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7e5d1e16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335560%26refer%3DShare&h=06efa650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=335560&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都有四單&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢單再望望港共正苦真係把幾火。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨就係咁， 陰啲陰啲就帶啲野送大禮。<br />\n<br />\n香港係大陸旅客流通最多嘅地區， 陳肇始堅稱未有數據顯示有引入豬 但係又冇公佈過任何數據話係關口做咗咩防疫 / 抽檢工作。 <br />\n<br />\n如果日本咁樣查都有四單， 咁姐係我地已經食咗好多病豬肉入肚都未頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係一個循環， 當年sars 又係中國送大禮之後懶係幫香港就搞到今時今日香港淪陷<br />\n<br />\n今次如果研究到病豬其實對人體有害嘅時候， 真係十條命都唔夠洗之餘 仲可以一炮過 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">換撚哂啲腥港人落嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線架 屌你老母香港特區政苦"},{"pid":"b45fc197b5c48f44b3b0b33f422ac2f43bfd169f","tid":996161,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"其實呢排唔好食豬啦"},{"pid":"721df636827ea38bd56f22897d5133919ae00765","tid":996161,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}